main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Caracas, Venezuela on December 5, 1965.
interesting points: The object was described as the size of a grapefruit and pinkish in color,The object exhibited a straight path about 50 degrees above the horizon,It was observed for one minute and showed no blinking lights or body markings,No physical evidence or photographs were recorded from the sighting, The sighting was evaluated as possibly a satellite, but the size and speed raised questions.
witness description: Observer from NASA with 23 years of flight experience
